- So, despite matching my dislike of overcompression, the live candidate sacrifices the disciplined, multitracked, studio‑polished AOR virtues (tight harmonies, controlled low end, transparent separation and cohesive sequencing) that make Born in the USA the better alignment with my stated tastes.

