  - Lead vocals are “clear … up front with natural room,” which aligns with my desire for intimate, close‑sounding vocals that nonetheless preserve room and air (rather than hyper‑close or overly glued multitracking).
  - The description notes tight rhythmic pockets, expressive solos, and tasteful piano/synth accents — these are the arrangement elements I value (groove, tasteful keys, solos that feel musical rather than showy detours).
